# No environment variables are required to run this project.
#
# Imagery is loaded from NASA GIBS (Blue Marble + VIIRS Black Marble), which
# does not require an access token. `Ion.defaultAccessToken = ''` is set in
# the Cesium viewer to disable the default Cesium Ion fetch.
#
# Live orbital data is fetched from the public Celestrak endpoints — no key.
#
# This file exists only to document the absence of secrets.
